        "timestamp": "2017-10-09 19:20:05.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1\n\nesr_vm_init.sh assumes the existence of /opt/config/esr_docker.txt. Files in /opt/config are created via Heat template at installation time. As such all the Heat templates and env files in Gerrit should be modified accordingly to have a new parameter. Also, the open-o VM section in all the heat templates should be extended to actually pass that parameter to the VM.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
