        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-10-10 13:26:08.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1\n\nThere is still something missing in the Heat templates (yaml files): you need to pass the esr docker version to the open-o VM.\n\nPlease go to the open-o section and add the following line in the \"user_data\" section:\n\n__esr_docker__: { get_param: esr_docker }\n\nThen, in the bash script below the user_data section, please add:\n\necho \"__esr_docker__\" > /opt/config/esr_docker.txt\n\nThanks",
        "patchset_number": 4
      },
